{
  "video_id": "-MTRxRO5SRA",
  "title": "Let's teach for mastery -- not test scores | Sal Khan",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12954.0,
      "end_time": 15904.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here today to talk about the two ideas that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15904.0,
      "end_time": 18286.0,
      "text": "at least based on my observations at Khan Academy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18286.0,
      "end_time": 22188.0,
      "text": "are kind of the core, or the key leverage points for learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22188.0,
      "end_time": 24228.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s the idea of mastery"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 24228.0,
      "end_time": 26037.0,
      "text": "and the idea of mindset."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26037.0,
      "end_time": 28895.0,
      "text": "I saw this in the early days working with my cousins."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28895.0,
      "end_time": 31399.0,
      "text": "A lot of them were having trouble with math at first,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31399.0,
      "end_time": 34477.0,
      "text": "because they had all of these gaps accumulated in their learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34477.0,
      "end_time": 37490.0,
      "text": "And because of that, at some point they got to an algebra class"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37490.0,
      "end_time": 40916.0,
      "text": "and they might have been a little bit shaky on some of the pre-algebra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40916.0,
      "end_time": 44385.0,
      "text": "and because of that, they thought they didn&#39;t have the math gene."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44385.0,
      "end_time": 46072.0,
      "text": "Or they&#39;d get to a calculus class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46072.0,
      "end_time": 48858.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;d be a little bit shaky on the algebra."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48858.0,
      "end_time": 50452.0,
      "text": "I saw it in the early days"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50452.0,
      "end_time": 54004.0,
      "text": "when I was uploading some of those videos on YouTube,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54004.0,
      "end_time": 57305.0,
      "text": "and I realized that people who were not my cousins were watching."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57305.0,
      "end_time": 59194.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59194.0,
      "end_time": 63084.0,
      "text": "And at first, those comments were just simple thank-yous."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 63084.0,
      "end_time": 65077.0,
      "text": "I thought that was a pretty big deal."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65077.0,
      "end_time": 67553.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know how much time you all spend on YouTube."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67553.0,
      "end_time": 69664.0,
      "text": "Most of the comments are not &quot;Thank you.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 69664.0,
      "end_time": 71145.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71145.0,
      "end_time": 72807.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re a little edgier than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 72807.0,
      "end_time": 75262.0,
      "text": "But then the comments got a little more intense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 75262.0,
      "end_time": 79742.0,
      "text": "student after student saying that they had grown up not liking math."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79742.0,
      "end_time": 82965.0,
      "text": "It was getting difficult as they got into more advanced math topics."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 82965.0,
      "end_time": 84517.0,
      "text": "By the time they got to algebra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 84517.0,
      "end_time": 87869.0,
      "text": "they had so many gaps in their knowledge they couldn&#39;t engage with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87869.0,
      "end_time": 89966.0,
      "text": "They thought they didn&#39;t have the math gene."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 89966.0,
      "end_time": 91470.0,
      "text": "But when they were a bit older,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 91470.0,
      "end_time": 93737.0,
      "text": "they took a little agency and decided to engage."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 93737.0,
      "end_time": 95613.0,
      "text": "They found resources like Khan Academy"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 95613.0,
      "end_time": 98787.0,
      "text": "and they were able to fill in those gaps and master those concepts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 98787.0,
      "end_time": 101401.0,
      "text": "and that reinforced their mindset that it wasn&#39;t fixed;"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101401.0,
      "end_time": 104990.0,
      "text": "that they actually were capable of learning mathematics."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104990.0,
      "end_time": 109067.0,
      "text": "And in a lot of ways, this is how you would master a lot of things in life."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109067.0,
      "end_time": 111390.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the way you would learn a martial art."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 111390.0,
      "end_time": 114580.0,
      "text": "In a martial art, you would practice the white belt skills"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114580.0,
      "end_time": 116017.0,
      "text": "as long as necessary,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 116017.0,
      "end_time": 117592.0,
      "text": "and only when you&#39;ve mastered it"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117592.0,
      "end_time": 119751.0,
      "text": "you would move on to become a yellow belt."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 119751.0,
      "end_time": 121846.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the way you learn a musical instrument:"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 121846.0,
      "end_time": 124164.0,
      "text": "you practice the basic piece over and over again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 124164.0,
      "end_time": 125776.0,
      "text": "and only when you&#39;ve mastered it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 125776.0,
      "end_time": 127471.0,
      "text": "you go on to the more advanced one."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 127471.0,
      "end_time": 128835.0,
      "text": "But what we point out --"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128835.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133344.0,
      "text": "this is not the way a traditional academic model is structured,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 133344.0,
      "end_time": 136703.0,
      "text": "the type of academic model that most of us grew up in."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136703.0,
      "end_time": 138269.0,
      "text": "In a traditional academic model,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 138269.0,
      "end_time": 140712.0,
      "text": "we group students together, usually by age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 140712.0,
      "end_time": 142015.0,
      "text": "and around middle school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 142015.0,
      "end_time": 143885.0,
      "text": "by age and perceived ability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 143885.0,
      "end_time": 147038.0,
      "text": "and we shepherd them all together at the same pace."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147038.0,
      "end_time": 148359.0,
      "text": "And what typically happens,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 148359.0,
      "end_time": 150884.0,
      "text": "let&#39;s say we&#39;re in a middle school pre-algebra class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 150884.0,
      "end_time": 152702.0,
      "text": "and the current unit is on exponents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 152702.0,
      "end_time": 154916.0,
      "text": "the teacher will give a lecture on exponents,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 154916.0,
      "end_time": 157225.0,
      "text": "then we&#39;ll go home, do some homework."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 157225.0,
      "end_time": 159303.0,
      "text": "The next morning, we&#39;ll review the homework,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 159303.0,
      "end_time": 161675.0,
      "text": "then another lecture, homework, lecture, homework."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 161675.0,
      "end_time": 163960.0,
      "text": "That will continue for about two or three weeks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 163960.0,
      "end_time": 165159.0,
      "text": "and then we get a test."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 165159.0,
      "end_time": 168501.0,
      "text": "On that test, maybe I get a 75 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 168501.0,
      "end_time": 169942.0,
      "text": "maybe you get a 90 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 169942.0,
      "end_time": 171950.0,
      "text": "maybe you get a 95 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 171950.0,
      "end_time": 174721.0,
      "text": "And even though the test identified gaps in our knowledge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 174721.0,
      "end_time": 176704.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know 25 percent of the material."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 176704.0,
      "end_time": 179700.0,
      "text": "Even the A student, what was the five percent they didn&#39;t know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 179700.0,
      "end_time": 181537.0,
      "text": "Even though we&#39;ve identified the gaps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 181537.0,
      "end_time": 184099.0,
      "text": "the whole class will then move on to the next subject,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 184099.0,
      "end_time": 187525.0,
      "text": "probably a more advanced subject that&#39;s going to build on those gaps."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 187525.0,
      "end_time": 190922.0,
      "text": "It might be logarithms or negative exponents."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 190922.0,
      "end_time": 193977.0,
      "text": "And that process continues, and you immediately start to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 193977.0,
      "end_time": 195176.0,
      "text": "how strange this is."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 195176.0,
      "end_time": 197971.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t know 25 percent of the more foundational thing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 197971.0,
      "end_time": 200440.0,
      "text": "and now I&#39;m being pushed to the more advanced thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 200440.0,
      "end_time": 204176.0,
      "text": "And this will continue for months, years, all the way until at some point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 204176.0,
      "end_time": 206640.0,
      "text": "I might be in an algebra class or trigonometry class"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 206640.0,
      "end_time": 207921.0,
      "text": "and I hit a wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 207921.0,
      "end_time": 210599.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s not because algebra is fundamentally difficult"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 210599.0,
      "end_time": 214615.0,
      "text": "or because the student isn&#39;t bright."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 214615.0,
      "end_time": 217950.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s because I&#39;m seeing an equation and they&#39;re dealing with exponents"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 217950.0,
      "end_time": 220703.0,
      "text": "and that 30 percent that I didn&#39;t know is showing up."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 220703.0,
      "end_time": 224469.0,
      "text": "And then I start to disengage."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 224469.0,
      "end_time": 227919.0,
      "text": "To appreciate how absurd that is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 227919.0,
      "end_time": 231124.0,
      "text": "imagine if we did other things in our life that way."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 231124.0,
      "end_time": 232602.0,
      "text": "Say, home-building."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 232602.0,
      "end_time": 236878.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 236878.0,
      "end_time": 240296.0,
      "text": "So we bring in the contractor and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 240296.0,
      "end_time": 242868.0,
      "text": "&quot;We were told we have two weeks to build a foundation."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 242868.0,
      "end_time": 244228.0,
      "text": "Do what you can.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 244228.0,
      "end_time": 246985.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 246985.0,
      "end_time": 248801.0,
      "text": "So they do what they can."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 248801.0,
      "end_time": 249981.0,
      "text": "Maybe it rains."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 249981.0,
      "end_time": 251974.0,
      "text": "Maybe some of the supplies don&#39;t show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 251974.0,
      "end_time": 255308.0,
      "text": "And two weeks later, the inspector comes, looks around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 255308.0,
      "end_time": 257997.0,
      "text": "says, &quot;OK, the concrete is still wet right over there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 257997.0,
      "end_time": 260838.0,
      "text": "that part&#39;s not quite up to code ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 260838.00000000003,
      "end_time": 262220.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll give it an 80 percent.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 262220.0,
      "end_time": 263308.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 263308.0,
      "end_time": 266067.0,
      "text": "You say, &quot;Great! That&#39;s a C. Let&#39;s build the first floor.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 266067.0,
      "end_time": 267109.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 267109.0,
      "end_time": 268287.0,
      "text": "Same thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 268287.0,
      "end_time": 272150.0,
      "text": "We have two weeks, do what you can, inspector shows up, it&#39;s a 75 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 272150.0,
      "end_time": 273333.0,
      "text": "Great, that&#39;s a D-plus."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 273333.0,
      "end_time": 274603.0,
      "text": "Second floor, third floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 274603.0,
      "end_time": 277405.0,
      "text": "and all of a sudden, while you&#39;re building the third floor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 277405.0,
      "end_time": 278865.0,
      "text": "the whole structure collapses."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 278865.0,
      "end_time": 282133.0,
      "text": "And if your reaction is the reaction you typically have in education,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 282133.0,
      "end_time": 283498.0,
      "text": "or that a lot of folks have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 283498.0,
      "end_time": 285628.0,
      "text": "you might say, maybe we had a bad contractor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 285628.0,
      "end_time": 288745.0,
      "text": "or maybe we needed better inspection or more frequent inspection."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 288745.0,
      "end_time": 291018.0,
      "text": "But what was really broken was the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 291018.0,
      "end_time": 294071.0,
      "text": "We were artificially constraining how long we had to something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 294071.0,
      "end_time": 296468.0,
      "text": "pretty much ensuring a variable outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 296468.0,
      "end_time": 300016.0,
      "text": "and we took the trouble of inspecting and identifying those gaps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 300016.0,
      "end_time": 301973.0,
      "text": "but then we built right on top of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 301973.0,
      "end_time": 304934.0,
      "text": "So the idea of mastery learning is to do the exact opposite."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 304934.0,
      "end_time": 307426.0,
      "text": "Instead of artificially constraining, fixing"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 307426.0,
      "end_time": 309438.0,
      "text": "when and how long you work on something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 309438.0,
      "end_time": 311680.0,
      "text": "pretty much ensuring that variable outcome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 311680.0,
      "end_time": 313980.0,
      "text": "the A, B, C, D, F --"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 313980.0,
      "end_time": 315844.0,
      "text": "do it the other way around."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 315844.0,
      "end_time": 317660.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s variable is when and how long"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 317660.0,
      "end_time": 319778.0,
      "text": "a student actually has to work on something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 319778.0,
      "end_time": 323445.0,
      "text": "and what&#39;s fixed is that they actually master the material."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 323445.0,
      "end_time": 325120.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s important to realize"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 325120.0,
      "end_time": 328509.0,
      "text": "that not only will this make the student learn their exponents better,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 328509.0,
      "end_time": 331491.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;ll reinforce the right mindset muscles."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 331491.0,
      "end_time": 334943.0,
      "text": "It makes them realize that if you got 20 percent wrong on something,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 334943.0,
      "end_time": 338356.0,
      "text": "it doesn&#39;t mean that you have a C branded in your DNA somehow."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 338356.0,
      "end_time": 340814.0,
      "text": "It means that you should just keep working on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 340814.0,
      "end_time": 343330.0,
      "text": "You should have grit; you should have perseverance;"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 343330.0,
      "end_time": 345908.0,
      "text": "you should take agency over your learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 345908.0,
      "end_time": 348922.0,
      "text": "Now, a lot of skeptics might say, well, hey, this is all great,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 348922.0,
      "end_time": 351667.0,
      "text": "philosophically, this whole idea of mastery-based learning"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 351667.0,
      "end_time": 353127.0,
      "text": "and its connection to mindset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 353127.0,
      "end_time": 355250.0,
      "text": "students taking agency over their learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 355250.0,
      "end_time": 358409.0,
      "text": "It makes a lot of sense, but it seems impractical."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 358409.0,
      "end_time": 361830.0,
      "text": "To actually do it, every student would be on their own track."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 361830.0,
      "end_time": 363478.0,
      "text": "It would have to be personalized,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 363478.0,
      "end_time": 366684.0,
      "text": "you&#39;d have to have private tutors and worksheets for every student."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 366684.0,
      "end_time": 368207.0,
      "text": "And these aren&#39;t new ideas --"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 368207.0,
      "end_time": 371057.0,
      "text": "there were experiments in Winnetka, Illinois, 100 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 371057.0,
      "end_time": 373899.0,
      "text": "where they did mastery-based learning and saw great results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 373899.0,
      "end_time": 377220.0,
      "text": "but they said it wouldn&#39;t scale because it was logistically difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 377220.0,
      "end_time": 380151.0,
      "text": "The teacher had to give different worksheets to every student,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 380151.0,
      "end_time": 381463.0,
      "text": "give on-demand assessments."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 381463.0,
      "end_time": 383748.0,
      "text": "But now today, it&#39;s no longer impractical."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 383748.0,
      "end_time": 385138.0,
      "text": "We have the tools to do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 385138.0,
      "end_time": 387757.0,
      "text": "Students see an explanation at their own time and pace?"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 387757.0,
      "end_time": 389376.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s on-demand video for that."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 389376.0,
      "end_time": 391472.0,
      "text": "They need practice? They need feedback?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 391472.0,
      "end_time": 396311.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s adaptive exercises readily available for students."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 396311.0,
      "end_time": 398929.0,
      "text": "And when that happens, all sorts of neat things happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 398929.0,
      "end_time": 401726.0,
      "text": "One, the students can actually master the concepts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 401726.0,
      "end_time": 403945.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re also building their growth mindset,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 403945.0,
      "end_time": 405766.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re building grit, perseverance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 405766.0,
      "end_time": 407813.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re taking agency over their learning."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 407813.0,
      "end_time": 410394.0,
      "text": "And all sorts of beautiful things can start to happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 410394.0,
      "end_time": 412054.0,
      "text": "in the actual classroom."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 412054.0,
      "end_time": 414136.0,
      "text": "Instead of it being focused on the lecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 414136.0,
      "end_time": 415978.0,
      "text": "students can interact with each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 415978.0,
      "end_time": 418160.0,
      "text": "They can get deeper mastery over the material."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 418160.0,
      "end_time": 420537.0,
      "text": "They can go into simulations, Socratic dialogue."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 420537.0,
      "end_time": 423240.0,
      "text": "To appreciate what we&#39;re talking about"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 423240.0,
      "end_time": 427311.0,
      "text": "and the tragedy of lost potential here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 427311.0,
      "end_time": 430985.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d like to give a little bit of a thought experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 430985.0,
      "end_time": 436075.0,
      "text": "If we were to go 400 years into the past to Western Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 436075.0,
      "end_time": 439263.0,
      "text": "which even then, was one of the more literate parts of the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 439263.0,
      "end_time": 443556.0,
      "text": "you would see that about 15 percent of the population knew how to read."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 443556.0,
      "end_time": 447218.0,
      "text": "And I suspect that if you asked someone who did know how to read,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 447218.0,
      "end_time": 449138.0,
      "text": "say a member of the clergy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 449138.0,
      "end_time": 452774.0,
      "text": "&quot;What percentage of the population do you think is even capable of reading?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 452774.0,
      "end_time": 456359.0,
      "text": "They might say, &quot;Well, with a great education system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 456359.0,
      "end_time": 459424.0,
      "text": "maybe 20 or 30 percent.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 459424.0,
      "end_time": 461035.0,
      "text": "But if you fast forward to today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 461035.0,
      "end_time": 464074.0,
      "text": "we know that that prediction would have been wildly pessimistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 464074.0,
      "end_time": 468223.0,
      "text": "that pretty close to 100 percent of the population is capable of reading."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 468223.0,
      "end_time": 471494.0,
      "text": "But if I were to ask you a similar question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 471494.0,
      "end_time": 475057.0,
      "text": "&quot;What percentage of the population do you think is capable"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 475057.0,
      "end_time": 477954.0,
      "text": "of truly mastering calculus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 477954.0,
      "end_time": 480991.0,
      "text": "or understanding organic chemistry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 480991.0,
      "end_time": 484301.0,
      "text": "or being able to contribute to cancer research?&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 484301.0,
      "end_time": 487222.0,
      "text": "A lot of you might say, &quot;Well, with a great education system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 487222.0,
      "end_time": 489778.0,
      "text": "maybe 20, 30 percent.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 489778.0,
      "end_time": 491115.0,
      "text": "But what if that estimate"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 491115.0,
      "end_time": 494526.0,
      "text": "is just based on your own experience in a non-mastery framework,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 494526.0,
      "end_time": 497382.0,
      "text": "your own experience with yourself or observing your peers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 497382.0,
      "end_time": 500195.0,
      "text": "where you&#39;re being pushed at this set pace through classes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 500195.0,
      "end_time": 501558.0,
      "text": "accumulating all these gaps?"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 501558.0,
      "end_time": 503223.0,
      "text": "Even when you got that 95 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 503223.0,
      "end_time": 505059.0,
      "text": "what was that five percent you missed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 505059.0,
      "end_time": 507810.0,
      "text": "And it keeps accumulating -- you get to an advanced class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 507810.0,
      "end_time": 509706.0,
      "text": "all of a sudden you hit a wall and say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 509706.0,
      "end_time": 511733.0,
      "text": "&quot;I&#39;m not meant to be a cancer researcher;"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 511733.0,
      "end_time": 514685.0,
      "text": "not meant to be a physicist; not meant to be a mathematician.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 514684.99999999994,
      "end_time": 516685.99999999994,
      "text": "I suspect that that actually is the case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 516686.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520536.00000000006,
      "text": "but if you were allowed to be operating in a mastery framework,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 520535.99999999994,
      "end_time": 523976.99999999994,
      "text": "if you were allowed to really take agency over your learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 523977.0,
      "end_time": 525597.0,
      "text": "and when you get something wrong,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 525597.0,
      "end_time": 528413.0,
      "text": "embrace it -- view that failure as a moment of learning --"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 528413.0,
      "end_time": 532394.0,
      "text": "that number, the percent that could really master calculus"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 532394.0,
      "end_time": 534178.0,
      "text": "or understand organic chemistry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 534178.0,
      "end_time": 537601.0,
      "text": "is actually a lot closer to 100 percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 537601.0,
      "end_time": 541019.0,
      "text": "And this isn&#39;t even just a &quot;nice to have.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 541019.0,
      "end_time": 543511.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s a social imperative."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 543511.0,
      "end_time": 547386.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re exiting what you could call the industrial age"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 547386.0,
      "end_time": 551646.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re going into this information revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 551646.0,
      "end_time": 553844.0,
      "text": "And it&#39;s clear that some things are happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 553844.0,
      "end_time": 555981.0,
      "text": "In the industrial age, society was a pyramid."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 555981.0,
      "end_time": 561085.0,
      "text": "At the base of the pyramid, you needed human labor."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 561085.0,
      "end_time": 564442.0,
      "text": "In the middle of the pyramid, you had an information processing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 564442.0,
      "end_time": 566064.0,
      "text": "a bureaucracy class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 566064.0,
      "end_time": 569762.0,
      "text": "and at the top of the pyramid, you had your owners of capital"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 569762.0,
      "end_time": 571785.0,
      "text": "and your entrepreneurs"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 571785.0,
      "end_time": 573904.0,
      "text": "and your creative class."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 573904.0,
      "end_time": 575724.0,
      "text": "But we know what&#39;s happening already,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 575724.0,
      "end_time": 577763.0,
      "text": "as we go into this information revolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 577763.0,
      "end_time": 580740.0,
      "text": "The bottom of that pyramid, automation, is going to take over."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 580740.0,
      "end_time": 583089.0,
      "text": "Even that middle tier, information processing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 583089.0,
      "end_time": 584739.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s what computers are good at."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 584739.0,
      "end_time": 586510.0,
      "text": "So as a society, we have a question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 586510.0,
      "end_time": 589652.0,
      "text": "All this new productivity is happening because of this technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 589652.0,
      "end_time": 591006.0,
      "text": "but who participates in it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 591006.0,
      "end_time": 594225.0,
      "text": "Is it just going to be that very top of the pyramid, in which case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 594225.0,
      "end_time": 595590.0,
      "text": "what does everyone else do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 595590.0,
      "end_time": 596780.0,
      "text": "How do they operate?"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 596780.0,
      "end_time": 599581.0,
      "text": "Or do we do something that&#39;s more aspirational?"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 599581.0,
      "end_time": 602715.0,
      "text": "Do we actually attempt to invert the pyramid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 602715.0,
      "end_time": 604740.0,
      "text": "where you have a large creative class,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 604740.0,
      "end_time": 608445.0,
      "text": "where almost everyone can participate as an entrepreneur,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 608445.0,
      "end_time": 610850.0,
      "text": "an artist, as a researcher?"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 610850.0,
      "end_time": 612804.0,
      "text": "And I don&#39;t think that this is utopian."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 612804.0,
      "end_time": 615192.0,
      "text": "I really think that this is all based on the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 615192.0,
      "end_time": 617400.0,
      "text": "that if we let people tap into their potential"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 617400.0,
      "end_time": 619388.0,
      "text": "by mastering concepts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 619388.0,
      "end_time": 622989.0,
      "text": "by being able to exercise agency over their learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 622989.0,
      "end_time": 624672.0,
      "text": "that they can get there."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 624672.0,
      "end_time": 628696.0,
      "text": "And when you think of it as just a citizen of the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 628696.0,
      "end_time": 629983.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s pretty exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 629983.0,
      "end_time": 632635.0,
      "text": "I mean, think about the type of equity we can we have,"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 632635.0,
      "end_time": 636339.0,
      "text": "and the rate at which civilization could even progress."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 636339.0,
      "end_time": 638576.0,
      "text": "And so, I&#39;m pretty optimistic about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 638576.0,
      "end_time": 642163.0,
      "text": "I think it&#39;s going to be a pretty exciting time to be alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 642163.0,
      "end_time": 643353.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 643353.0,
      "end_time": 653353.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}